# .actrc — default flags for `act` (local GitHub Actions simulation)
# https://github.com/nektos/act
#
# Run workflows locally:
#   act push                              # simulate push event, all workflows
#   act push -W .github/workflows/capacitor-android.yml   # one workflow
#
# The ubuntu-latest runner is mapped to our custom Android image (built locally).
# Build it first with: just docker-build
#
# .secrets.local is gitignored — copy .secrets.local.example and fill in values.

-P ubuntu-latest=holy-echoes-android:latest
--secret-file .secrets.local
--pull=false
--env GITHUB_REPOSITORY_OWNER=joeboylson
--env GITHUB_REPOSITORY=joeboylson/holy-echoes
--artifact-server-path /tmp/act-artifacts
